  "time_ut": 1662305588,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95  \u0b90.\u0ba4\u0bc7.\u0b95 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "United Nations will emerge as a strong party",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party's Ratnapura district organizer S. Ananthakumar has said that the party will be strengthened again with the 76th National Conference of the United National Party and will work with dedication to find solutions to all kinds of economic problems faced by the people.",
        "He also mentioned that only President Ranil Wickremesinghe can build the country's economy.",
        "The 76th National Conference of the party will be held on the 6th in a grand manner at Sugatadasa Indoor Stadium in Colombo under the leadership of party leader Ranil Wickramavinga.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe, the contemporary leader of this traditional party, which was the oldest party in Sri Lanka and the leading party in getting the country's independence, mentioned that as the president of the country, he is promoting good governance and working with a vision to build the economy.",
        "He also pointed out that President Ranil Wickremesinghe has given the power to breathe again to Sri Lanka, which is reeling under severe economic crisis.",
        "He said that the President is also engaged in activities to re-strengthen the rule of law which was in disarray in the country and unite all parties to form an all-party government.",
        "Celebrating its 76th year, the United Nations is the premier party in the development and introduction of sound economic policies in this country.",
        "He pointed out that the cost of living of the people of the country was very low during the last period of good governance and due to improper administration, the country was pushed into the economic abyss.",
        "The statement mentioned that the President has convinced the people of the country through his mid-term budget and concrete resolutions that only the United Nations can stabilize the economy."
      ],
